{"prompt": "Build a user-friendly e-commerce store for a gourmet coffee brand. The design should prominently display a rich espresso brown.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Gourmet Coffee Co.</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #4a2c2a; /* Espresso Brown */\n            --secondary-color: #8c6b5f; /* Lighter brown for accents */\n            --text-color: #ffffff;\n            --button-text-color: #ffffff;\n            --footer-bg: #331f1f;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f4f1ed;\n            color: #333;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--primary-color), var(--secondary-color));\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n\n        header p {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            margin-top: 5px;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 90%;\n            max-width: 1200px;\n            margin: 20px auto;\n            padding: 20px;\n            background-color: var(--text-color);\n            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n        }\n\n        h2 {\n            text-align: center;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .product-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .product-item {\n            border: 1px solid var(--secondary-color);\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            padding: 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n            background-color: #fff;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .product-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n\n        .product-item img {\n            max-width: 100%;\n            height: 200px;\n            object-fit: cover;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            border: 1px solid var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        .product-item h3 {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n        }\n\n        .product-item p {\n            font-size: 0.95em;\n            color: #555;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n        }\n\n        .product-item .price {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .add-to-cart-btn {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: var(--button-text-color);\n            border: none;\n            padding: 12px 25px;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-size: 1em;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .add-to-cart-btn:hover {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--footer-bg);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <h1>Gourmet Coffee Co.</h1>\n        <p>Experience the Richness of Handcrafted Coffee</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <h2>Our Signature Blends</h2>\n        <div class=\"product-grid\">\n            <div class=\"product-item\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/4a2c2a/ffffff?text=Espresso+Roast\" alt=\"Espresso Roast Coffee\">\n                <h3>Espresso Roast</h3>\n                <p>Bold and intense, perfect for your morning espresso.</p>\n                <div class=\"price\">$18.99</div>\n                <button class=\"add-to-cart-btn\">Add to Cart</button>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"product-item\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/4a2c2a/ffffff?text=Medium+Roast\" alt=\"Medium Roast Coffee\">\n                <h3>Medium Roast</h3>\n                <p>Smooth and balanced, with notes of caramel.</p>\n                <div class=\"price\">$16.99</div>\n                <button class=\"add-to-cart-btn\">Add to Cart</button>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"product-item\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/4a2c2a/ffffff?text=Light+Roast\" alt=\"Light Roast Coffee\">\n                <h3>Light Roast</h3>\n                <p>Bright and fruity, a delightful start to your day.</p>\n                <div class=\"price\">$15.99</div>\n                <button class=\"add-to-cart-btn\">Add to Cart</button>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"product-item\">\n                <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/4a2c2a/ffffff?text=Decaf\" alt=\"Decaf Coffee\">\n                <h3>Decaf Delight</h3>\n                <p>Full flavor, without the caffeine kick.</p>\n                <div class=\"price\">$17.99</div>\n                <button class=\"add-to-cart-btn\">Add to Cart</button>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Gourmet Coffee Co. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}